 <li><a href="/content/dam/facilities-management-development/environmental-health-safety/docs/kitchen-inspection-checklist.pdf"><span class="sr-only">PDF file</span>kitchen<span aria-hidden="true" class="autoIconLink fa fa-file-pdf-o"></span></a></li> 
