                    <div class="panel-body ">
                        <div class="1504042432445 stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="8f142726-f6af-47c0-b75b-98d731d12915" >

    <p>Inspection teams are expected to transfer the information from the Workplace Inspection Hazard Reporting Form to the <a href="/content/dam/facilities-management-development/environmental-health-safety/docs/inspection-summary-report.xlsx"><span class="sr-only">excel file</span>Inspection Summary Report<span aria-hidden="true" class="autoIconLink fa fa-file-excel-o"></span></a>. Your report should:</p> 
<ul> 
 <li>specifically describe hazards, including location;</li> 
 <li>categorize hazards and identify risks;</li> 
 <li>recommend controls;</li> 
 <li>identify who should receive the report;</li> 
 <li>specify response time (e.g. 21 days); and</li> 
 <li>include follow-up protocol.</li> 
</ul> 
<p>Inspection teams should ensure that all class "A" Hazard (high risk) items are addressed immediately and that controls are in place.</p>
    





</div>
